 JDBC database URL for sql server
 ------------------------------------
 -jdbc:sql server://[serverName[\instanceName][:portNumber]]
  [;property=value[;proporty=value]]
 -serverName - host name or ip address of the machine on which sql server is running.
 -instanceName - name of instance to connect to the serverName. The dfault instance is used iff this parameter is not specified.
 -portNumber - portNumber of the SQL server,  the default is 1433. 
 - property=value - specify one or more additional connection property.
